description:
By now you would think girls would learn not to be late to any class The Master is teaching. But Sadly for Entice she has not learned this lesson.
Because of her tardiness The Master is going to teach her a lesson she will never forget… Never escape from.
The Master will ensure Entice is never late again… He will transform her into a robot and make sure she submits to his horny pleasures… He will have her cum again and again.
title: Master of The Class
